sinks.name: Sink1
sinks.script:
sink(input(
		Column_1 as string,
		Column_2 as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> Sink1

typeProperties.script:
section Section1;
shared DelimitedText3 = let
  AdfDoc = AzureStorage.BlobContents("https://test66666.blob.core.windows.net/testwrangle/HyperV-PhysicalServers.csv"),
  Csv = Csv.Document(AdfDoc, [Delimiter = ",", Encoding = TextEncoding.Utf8, QuoteStyle = QuoteStyle.Csv])
in
  Csv;
shared UserQuery = let
  Source = DelimitedText3,
  #"Removed columns" = Table.RemoveColumns(Source, {"Column1"})
in
  #"Removed columns";
